@ECHO OFF
TITLE %~n0
SETLOCAL

ECHO Start checking for updates
REM UsoClient StartScan

ECHO Start downloading Updates
REM UsoClient StartDownload

ECHO Start installing the downloaded updates
REM UsoClient StartInstall

ECHO Restart your device after installing the updates
REM UsoClient RestartDevice

ECHO Check, download and install updates
UsoClient ScanInstallWait

PAUSE

ENDLOCAL
